text: Jaime Paz Zamora (born April 15, 1939) is a Bolivian politician. He was President of Bolivia from August 6, 1989 to August 6, 1993. He was vice- president between 1982 and 1984. ==References== Category:1939 births Category:Presidents of Bolivia Category:Vice presidents of Bolivia Category:Living people
